JARVIS AI Mobile Assistant (Multi-Tenant SaaS Platform)
Project Goal

Develop a mobile AI assistant platform similar to JARVIS that runs as an Android application with a floating avatar widget, powered by a centralized SaaS backend.

The system must support multi-tenant architecture, meaning each user has their own assistant configuration and data isolated by tenant ID.

The mobile assistant must support:

voice interaction

wake word detection

customizable avatar

customizable voice

backend AI responses

knowledge retrieval

simple automation tasks

The backend infrastructure will be fully controlled and hosted by us.

рҹҡҖ Development Scope
Phase 1

Core assistant features.

Features:

Flutter mobile app

Floating avatar widget

Wake word detection

Speech-to-text

Gemini AI integration

Text-to-speech response

Knowledge queries

Question answering

Supported commands:

ask general questions

ask about knowledge base

basic conversational interaction

Phase 2

Automation features.

Add support for:

open installed apps

set reminders

perform internet searches

