рҹ“ұ Mobile Features
Login and Signup

Users create accounts inside the app.

Signup request:

POST /auth/signup

Backend creates:

tenant_id
assistant_config
рҹҺӣ Dashboard (Inside Mobile App)

Users must be able to customize the assistant.

Settings:

avatar image
wake word
voice gender
assistant name

Example UI:

Assistant Dashboard

Avatar
Wake Word
Voice Gender

[ Turn ON Assistant ]
рҹ–ј Avatar System

Users upload an avatar.

Process:

Upload image вҶ’ backend вҶ’ object storage

Database stores:

avatar_url

Mobile app loads avatar dynamically.

рҹҺӨ Wake Word Detection

The assistant must listen for a wake phrase.

Example:

Hey Jarvis
Hello Nova

The wake word must be:

configurable per tenant

The mobile app fetches wake word from backend config.

Possible implementation options:

Option 1 (MVP):

continuous speech_to_text listening
detect wake phrase

Option 2 (recommended):

Porcupine wake word engine
рҹҺӨ Speech Recognition

Use Flutter plugin:

speech_to_text

Workflow:

wake word detected
вҶ’ start STT
вҶ’ convert speech to text
рҹ”Ҡ Text-to-Speech

Use:

flutter_tts

Voice must be selected based on:

voice_gender

Options:

male
female

The voice must not be hardcoded.

The mobile app should dynamically select system voices.

