рҹҸў Multi-Tenant System

Each user must have a unique tenant.

Example:

tenant_id = UUID

All resources are linked to this tenant.

Example:

Tenant A

avatar
wake word
knowledge
conversations

Tenant B

avatar
wake word
knowledge
conversations
