tenant_id
assistant_name
avatar_url
wake_word
voice_gender
language
personality_prompt
Knowledge Base
knowledge_entries
-----------------
tenant_id
title
content
embedding

Used for RAG retrieval.

Conversations
conversations
-------------
tenant_id
query
response
timestamp
рҹ§  AI Engine

The AI system must support multi-provider LLM fallback.

Default LLM

Primary provider:

Gemini API

Example model:

gemini-1.5-flash
Fallback Provider

If Gemini fails:

Use:

OpenRouter
model: gpt-4o-mini

Flow:

User Query
    в”Ӯ
    в–ј
Gemini API
    в”Ӯ
    в”ң success вҶ’ return response
    в”Ӯ
    в”” failure
         в–ј
     OpenRouter
         в–ј
     GPT-4o-mini
вҡҷпёҸ Backend APIs
Authentication
POST /auth/signup
POST /auth/login
Assistant Configuration
GET /assistant/config
POST /assistant/config

Returns:

assistant_name
avatar_url
wake_word
voice_gender
Voice Query
POST /agent/query

Example request:

{
 "tenant_id": "abc123",
 "query": "What services do you offer?"
}

Example response:

{
 "response": "We offer AI development services."
}
рҹ“ҡ Knowledge Queries

User asks:

"What are your services?"

Backend performs:

vector search
retrieve knowledge
inject context
send to LLM

This enables tenant-specific knowledge assistants.

