рҹҺҜ Final Expected Result

The system should allow users to:

Download the mobile assistant app

Sign up inside the app

Customize their assistant

Activate a floating avatar

Trigger assistant using wake word

Ask questions and receive voice responses

Execute simple tasks

All data and AI processing must be handled by the central SaaS backend controlled by the platform owner.